Source code for http://www.windowsphone.com/en-gb/store/app/uk-trains/ef62d461-861c-4a9f-9198-8768532cc6aa

Description:
UK Trains brings you train departure information for all UK national rail stations.
New in 1.1:
* Allow to filter by destination
* Allow to pin stations to start screen
* Show walk directions to station
* Refresh location in background
* Compress HTTP requests
* Fix crash when app resumes into a station page after tombstoning

Keywords:
Train
Rail
Schedule
Departures
